query:
UPDATE enrollments SET classTime = CASE 
  WHEN classTime = '9am' THEN '9:00 AM'
  WHEN classTime = '10am' THEN '10:00 AM'
  WHEN classTime = '2pm' THEN '2:00 PM'
  WHEN classTime = '3pm' THEN '3:00 PM'
  WHEN classTime = '4pm' THEN '4:00 PM'
  WHEN classTime = '5pm' THEN '5:00 PM'
  WHEN classTime = '12pm' THEN '12:00 PM'
  WHEN classTime = '1pm' THEN '1:00 PM'
  ELSE classTime
END WHERE classTime IS NOT NULL;
